fulltitle: Life Is So Good!: The Complete Show
title: Life Is So Good!: The Complete Show
_filename: B:\Projects\maude\Beige\Life Is So Good! - The Complete Show.mp4
description:
For Beige's monthly performance in June of 2013, the group put together a show of sketches that were all linked. Here is the entire show presented as one video. Enjoy!

Beige is:

WRITERS: Alene Latimer, James McCarthy, Jon Bershad, Kerry O'Brien, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, Zack Phillips

ACTORS: Avery Monsen, Dan Hodapp, Jonathan Marballi, Kelly Hudson, Langan Kingsley, Lisa Kleinman

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, June 3, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
